{"tid":1794061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明明話罷買罷消費攬炒經濟，點解一車車港豬走去排隊埋紅底人血饅頭Pepe公仔","createTime":"2019-12-23T00:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T00:34:01.000Z","uid":60916,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"538dcba59da9e4f332c040f2f17bc27769f756a2","tid":1794061,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:27:55.000Z","msg":"唔肯罷工都算數唔屌<br />\n8月時講既罷消費罷買攬炒經濟<br />\n你地都唔肯做都算<br />\n仲要去買件人血饅頭Pepe<br />\n都算<br />\n買之前好多人講間野係中資<br />\n你地仲要狗沖去買<br />\n係咪買完就等於自己有參與場抗爭打卡拎光環<br />\n<br />\n咁樣既心態同5年有咩分別<br />\n咪一鳩樣<br />\n想贏<br />\n下世啦香港人<br />\n勇武既唔好再保護班和理非同香港人啦<br />\n當你condom咋"},{"pid":"ef9fe076ed87a0d9a79e352bfd1dfed7c62acc35","tid":1794061,"uid":198590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:27:58.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#60916 - 山齊士超級綠洲</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>12月1遊行有200萬人,我派Lm既連登仔,每人2000蚊,絕不走數 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>投完票贏完啦<br />\n仲唔出嚟</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1761734/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1761734/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">懷疑製造派錢假象 <blockquote><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/dA8N0Lx.png\" /></blockquote></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>不如幫幫白鴿黨裝修 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>11年同15年屌人民力量同熱血公民票<br />\n今日就鳩沙田友既票<br />\n咁就送左席比民賤聯<br />\n道歉Sorry好撚假囉<br />\n人地議席就無左咩都無<br />\n你地今次就大勝食咁多議席<br />\n仲要好多區比你地逼到退選讓路含淚投<br />\n<br />\n既然你地食人血饅頭食得咁開心<br />\n手足陣間不如發夢去是旦一個白鴿黨既辦事署裝下修<br />\n反正你地今次賺咁多經費咁多人工<br />\n比2條路你地揀<br />\n裝修/捐一半人工做抗爭基金<br />\n就係咁</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1753849/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1753849/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>新口號同洗腦金句！想贏既入嚟同我宣傳出去 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>將香港人 反抗<br />\n變做<br />\n香港人 返工<br />\n成個口號幾撚震撼</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1692157/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1692157/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>保護休班警,你我有責 - #4</code><br />\n<blockquote>唔好搞休班警<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1692143/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1692143/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>其實借運動識女溝女有咩問題 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>CCtai班友仔做咩咁敏感<br />\n大家都係有相同興趣同諗法<br />\n傾得埋再交換contact上埋床有咩問題<br />\nCCTai班小朋友真係大驚小怪</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1669147/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1669147/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/AwtAz1F.png\" />"},{"pid":"d0af328b4cf6e3029554bf3d0d3fe3e618a6419b","tid":1794061,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef9fe076ed87a0d9a79e352bfd1dfed7c62acc35","tid":1794061,"uid":198590,